"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-30-coco-gauff-bursts-tears-total-meltdown-crashes-paris-olympics-21326750\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"US flagbearer Coco Gauff claimed she was 'getting cheated' by poor decisions as she was dumped out of the women's singles competition at theParisOlympics with a 7-6 6-2 defeat to Donna Vekic.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 2, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9921841036770821, \"rank\": 0.004706377303060203, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Veki\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999518918241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Donna Vekic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Veki\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Veki\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this afternoon's tightly contested third-round clash at Roland-Garros, Vekic had a golden opportunity to pull away, with the Croatian leading 40-30 on Gauff's serve in the second set - and the point proved hugely contentious.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998980852122, \"rank\": 7.076810497884765e-08, \"text\": \"Croatian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It came after Gauff, the reigning US Open champion, had managed to throw away a 5-2 advantage in a dramatic first set.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.935861658826044, \"rank\": 0.027464247762228403, \"text\": \"US Open\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Gauff, trailing 3-2, moved backwards to hit a backhand near the baseline, the linesperson appeared to call the ball out before the American had swung her racket, causing her to miss.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997161451316803, \"rank\": 0.00018680555086758176, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the chair umpire, Jaume Campistol, took a different view, overruling the original decision before awarding the point to Vekic, putting the 28-year-old just two games away from victory.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A heated discussion then ensued between Gauff and Campistol, which resulted in the world number two breaking down in tears and accusing the officials of 'cheating' her out of a potential victory.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Campistol held firm on his decision and Vekic - a semi-finalist at Wimbledon earlier this summer - went on to wrap up the win in emphatic fashion to secure a place in the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GAUFF  'I was going back to hit the ball and he called it out before I hit it.'\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"UMPIRE  'You understand that I have to take a decision and in this case\\u2026'  GAUFF  'But you have to be sure\\u2026'  UMPIRE  'I am 100 per cent sure in this case.'\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GAUFF  'You are not, you just said maybe I am wrong!'\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"UMPIRE  'Based on your reaction I might be wrong.'\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GAUFF  'I never argue these calls but he called it out before I hit the ball.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It always happens to me on this court!\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Call the supervisor.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It always happens to me, every time.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You understand that I always have to advocate for myself, all the time.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am getting cheated in this game.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You guys are not fair to me.'\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Croatian No.13 seed Vekic saw off Italy's Lucia Bronzetti and Canada's Bianca Andreescu to secure her place in the third round against Gauff.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998980852122, \"rank\": 7.076810497884765e-08, \"text\": \"Croatian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999744832379792, \"rank\": 2.0465952635274326e-05, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2019, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucia_Bronzetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lucia Bronzetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucia_Bronzetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucia_Bronzetti\"}, {\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9178189505330949, \"rank\": 0.07048304501286025, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Andreescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bianca Andreescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Andreescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Andreescu\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Andreescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bianca Andreescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Andreescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Andreescu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff must now turn her attentions to the first round of the mixed doubles competition, in which she is representing the United States alongside Taylor Fritz.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9999966521687944, \"rank\": 3.3400725259208885e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Fritz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American duo begin their campaign with a potentially tricky first-round tie against Maximo Gonzalez and Nadia Podoroska of Argentina.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2284, \"end\": 2292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997161451316803, \"rank\": 0.00018680555086758176, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"score\": 0.9999999983701855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maximo Gonzalez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\"}, {\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Podoroska\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadia Podoroska\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Podoroska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Podoroska\"}, {\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991322510893557, \"rank\": 0.0005109206407578243, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff is also due to compete in the women's doubles competition with Jessica Pegula, with the pair handed a first-round match against Australia's Daria Saville and Ellen Perez.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Pegula\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Pegula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Pegula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Pegula\"}, {\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8532516058558156, \"rank\": 0.1716415134917813, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daria Saville\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\"}, {\"begin\": 2583, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellen Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An emotional Gauff called on tennis authorities to take inspiration from football and introduce a 'VAR system' as she addressed the contentious call shortly after her defeat to Vekic.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I felt that they called it before I hit.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think the ref disagreed.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think he just thought it did not, like, affect my swing, which I felt like it did,' Gauff told The Athletic.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Athletic\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There have been multiple times this year where that happened to me where I feel like I always have to be an advocate for myself on the court.\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I feel like in tennis, we should have a VAR system because these points are big deals.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Usually, afterwards they apologise.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's kind of frustrating when the sorry does not help you once the match is over.\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not fair at all.'\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sente